result.name: Imputed phased whole genome SNP variants for 163 vervet monkeys
result.description: Callset of filtered imputed and phased biallelic SNP genotypes of 163 vervet monkeys (genus Chlorocebus) from several African and Caribbean countries as described in Svardal et al. Nature Genetics 2017. Sample information can be found in Data S1 of Svardal et al. 2017.
